20_36	0.0	Whether that is true should become clear in 5 or 10 years, scientists with the fisheries service said.
20_37	0.0	One option, they said, would be to wait.
20_38	0.0	But other experts, including Bowles, said the answer was as apparent now as it would ever be.
20_39	0.18181818181818182	The fisheries service said any delay would increase the likelihood that some stocks of Snake River salmon would become extinct.
20_40	0.875	Pacific salmon are different from Atlantic salmon in that there are several species, and that different populations spawn at different times.
20_41	0.0	Moreover, they spawn only once and then die (Atlantic salmon, and steelhead, can return to the ocean and spawn again, several times).
